    <keyword>FTP</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC describes an Internet background file transfer service that is built upon the third-party transfer model of FTP.  No new protocols are involved.  The purpose of this memo is to stimulate discussions on new Internet service modes.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
